input_str: Hello, Victor Spiresau, one of the few new arrivals that photographers and MPs found off a New Year's Day flight from Romania. His moment of fame is over and he vanishes into the shadowlands of Britain's serf-labour force. He joins that great army of the underpaid to clean, care and cater.
